Abstract = {In the dynamic field of web development, the integration of
   sophisticated AI technologies for query processing has become
   increasingly crucial. This paper presents a framework that significantly
   improves the relevance of web query responses by leveraging cutting-edge
   technologies like We explore and compare the performance of both PaLM
