   Futurewei Technologies Inc; Google LLC; Dartmouth College},
Abstract = {This paper introduces Cellular-X, an LLM-powered agent designed to
   automate cellular base station (BS) maintenance. Leveraging multimodal
   LLM and retrieval-augmented generation (RAG) techniques, Cellular-X
   significantly enhances field engineer efficiency by quickly interpreting
   user intents, retrieving relevant technical information, and configuring
   a BS through iterative self-correction. Key features of the demo include
   automatic customized BS setup, document-based query answering, and
   voice-controlled configuration reporting and revision. We implemented
   Cellular-X on a USRP X310 testbed for demonstration. Demo videos and
   implementation details are available at
