Year = {2026},
Volume = {34},
Month = {JUN},
Abstract = {The latest version of AI-KM represents a significant upgrade to a
   comprehensive platform that seamlessly integrates knowledge management,
   intelligent Q\&A, and task automation. The update introduces a modular
   architecture and enhanced workflow engine as its core innovation,
   substantially lowering the barrier for users to access advanced AI
   functionalities. The system features strengthened support for
   Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) and automated testing, while also
   integrating Model Context Protocol (MCP) service invocation for extended
   connectivity. Through expert workflows, novice users can effortlessly
   execute complex tasks such as sophisticated querying and planning
   problem, effectively enhancing organizational knowledge accumulation,
   collaboration efficiency, and the reliability of Q\&A systems.},
