   Nguyen, Tu Anh Hoang; Nguyen, Quang-Dieu; Nguyen, Harius M.; Nguyen, Loan T. T., Vietnam Natl Univ, Ho Chi Minh City 700000, Vietnam.
   Nguyen, Alfred Hoang, FPT Univ, Fac Informat Technol, Ho Chi Minh City 71300, Vietnam.},
