   Processing-ICONIP-Annual, Auckland, NEW ZEALAND, DEC 02-06, 2024},
Abstract = {In this study, we present the design and development of a Generative AI
   service, Big Data Assistant (BD Assistant), leveraging generative AI to
   optimize marketing strategies for Samsung Electronics. By integrating
   customer data of Demographics, device ownership, behavior, and
   preferences, our AI-driven system automatically extracts customer
   segments for targeted campaigns in real-time. This approach employs
   advanced machine learning techniques, including Large Language Models
   (LLM) and explainable AI, to ensure precise and interpretable
   segmentation results. Through comprehensive analysis and validation, our
   system demonstrates significant improvements in campaign effectiveness
   and customer engagement, paving the way for data-driven marketing
   strategies that adapt to evolving consumer behaviors. The findings
   highlight the potential of AI in revolutionizing target marketing
   systems, offering a scalable solution for personalized and dynamic
   marketing strategies.},
