Note = {20th International Conference on Data Science-ICDATA, Las Vegas, NV, JUL
   22-25, 2024},
Abstract = {Establishing a social media presence and engaging with current trends
   within a specific domain is crucial for companies to emerge as thought
   leaders in their respective spaces. In this study, we have answered the
   question: Can small businesses with limited marketing resources use
   Generative Artificial.
   Intelligence (GAI) to quickly identify domain-specific trends, optimize
   content creation and personalize marketing strategies? To address this
   question, we developed a Large Language Model (LLM)-powered marketing
   agent to autonomously generate social media posts aligned with trending
   news and social media topics. Results show that this agent can
   significantly increase social media post frequency. This paper
   demonstrates the practical application of GAI in dynamic marketing
   environments and sets a precedent for similar innovations in various
   industries.},
